                    "description": "BK Group is a multidisciplinary firm built on the foundation of a number of predecessor institutions. Our major heritage firms \u2013 BK Corporate International, Exclusive Company Management, Scandinavian Corporate Services and Trust Alliance \u2013 were each closely tied to innovations in the specialized financial services industry. \n\nAs BK Group does today, these firms served a global client base of FTSE 100 companies, AIM quoted enterprises, private equity and real estate investment funds, multinational (\"blue-chip\") companies, the world's most prominent international financial institutions, pension funds, endowments and foundations, sovereign wealth funds, owner-managed businesses, expatriates, as well as high net-worth and ultra-high net-worth individuals, their families, other beneficiaries and circles of support.\n\nFor clients seeking the sophistication and quality of a large firm and the responsiveness and efficiency of a specialized boutique, we fill a distinctive niche. Clients know they can rely on our expertise and counsel, and that we are available whenever and wherever they need us. \n\nWe assist clients with corporate, institutional and private wealth matters of all sizes and complexity. We tend to establish long-term relationships with our clients, and take a holistic and intimate view of their specific needs, that may extend far beyond a particular structuring or transaction. As stewards of our principals' assets, we often become truly integrated into the fabric of our clients' businesses \u2013 functioning as an off-site counsel and partner. Clients view us not only as their service provider, but as a sounding board for ideas on how to preserve and grow their private wealth and corporate or institutional success.",
